# argocd

## CLI

## Connect through port-forward
$ argocd --port-forward --port-forward-namespace MYNAMESPACE app list

## Diff app with local changes
$ argocd --port-forward --port-forward-namespace MYNAMESPACE app diff MY_APP_NAME --hard-refresh --exit-code=false --loglevel error --server-side-generate --local $(pwd)


