Try:
- Set controller log level to debug
- Search for "Requesting app refresh caused by object update"
- Make a pie chart by `Kind`

## Get a list of all Kinds of resources ArgoCD manages

```sh
$ argocd app list -o name \
  xargs -n1 -I{} argocd app get {} -o json \
  | jq -r '.status.resources[]? | "\((.group // "core"))/\(.kind)"'
```
